{"type": "article", "id": 26008, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-27T07:06:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26767, "name": "Duplex"}, {"id": 26768, "name": "ARiNA"}, {"id": 26769, "name": "Drill"}, {"id": 26770, "name": "Autographer"}, {"id": 26772, "name": "Killexir Poison"}, {"id": 26793, "name": "Light & Free"}, {"id": 26799, "name": "Percha"}, {"id": 26773, "name": "MUT"}, {"id": 26774, "name": "MUEMMA"}, {"id": 26775, "name": "LeviSarha"}, {"id": 11422, "name": "达能"}, {"id": 26794, "name": "Dragon Rouge"}, {"id": 26777, "name": "James Wood"}, {"id": 26778, "name": "Rahul Shirbhate"}, {"id": 26800, "name": "Rafael Fernández"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120020rTnC5NP12KzbMYyI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Duplex by MUT</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这是一组由 <a href=\"http://www.mutdesign.com/\">MUT</a> 为西班牙公司 <a href=\"http://www.sancal.com/\">Sancal</a> 所打造的组合桌，富有现代感的设计风格让人能够将它们同设计师密斯·凡·德·罗（Mies van der Rohe）和建筑大师弗兰克·劳埃德·赖特（Frank Lloyd Wright）的作品联系起来。多层的结构美观大方，可动的托架也添加了实用性，适用于任何场合。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133011jpaskA5bfgH7FWDS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133011uCiRZPtq7KMQwelp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133011F87A9qeDk0TStVwI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133012Anbd75DaC9XxeYMi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86797066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133013dkHpEX2KY7PRxZWj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81540342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330133EQTDSIitMOKjB6b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>ARiNA by MUEMMA</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这款蓝牙音箱名为 <a href=\"http://www.muemma.com/collections/all/products/arina-speaker-gainsboro-set\" target=\"_blank\">ARiNA</a>，由柏林 MUEMMA 旗下的设计师设计，外观让人联想到苹果公司在美国加州库比蒂诺市（Cupertino）那个酷似飞碟的新总部 Campus2。音箱内部装有 6 个扩音器，可以实现 360 度的环绕音效。值得一提的是，音箱外套还提供了几种颜色和材质供用户更换，在不使用的时候还可以在中间放上手机，当作一个小摆设。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133013i8DAOVzwW2n3QoeU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133014b9QUa5BW8CTl6dFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133014u7fKYDZcCGwzB5AS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133015C4wcTijK5Lh1JByD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133015jftGoQEeRzsuU8VK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133015lUKcvEPq4r5iOf06.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Drill by LeviSarha</h2>\n<p class=\"\">比利时设计组合 <a href=\"http://levisarha.com/\" target=\"_blank\">LeviSarha</a> 推出的这款台灯名叫 Drill，由在当地颇为常见的玄武岩所制成。设计师 Levi Dethier 和 Sarha Duquesne 使用岩芯钻将一段圆柱形的部分取出，组装后的造型传递出了一股极简的风格。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133016wSeGc5VlhvUiZxjd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133016qGrPSWLdFcU7M9X0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133017iPGCTuYbNSsZLqIn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133017JpbSaCzmkcjPy5q3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133018Q62Z0SCxJ3Mk7Ivz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Autographer by James Wood</h2>\n<p class=\"\">GoPro 或许有了竞争对手，它叫 Autographer：这是一款由 James Wood 设计的可穿戴相机。相机盖的选择丰富，提供多种颜色的皮革或是帆布覆面，让人能够根据服饰进行自由搭配，增添时尚的气息。而在不使用的时候，只要轻轻旋转，就能起到保护镜头的作用。相机底座的夹子则有四种造型供用户挑选，适用于各种拍摄场合。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133018VyShCruG9xdtwqfU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330194OxLzD8luNgwPaIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133019YpVkLEGR7iaWz6KS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133020eLKxlJiZPmGM4Ykr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133020UBjzpq1gyVrGuklM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.36\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Light &amp; Free by Dragon Rouge</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这是 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://dragonrouge.com/\">Dragon Rouge</a> 伦敦分部为达能新推出的希腊式酸奶系列 Light &amp; Free 所设计的包装。为了突出酸奶中包含的真实果粒成分，包装的正面是五款相应的水果，搭配简笔画的女性轮廓，强调了产品的健康。背面则将水果和日常生活用品结合在一起，透露出年轻的气息，整体颇为吸睛。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133021QfpJlqNRM3x52U1D.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133022V1nwvaRrd2S5W6cq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133022LKawegYRyAp8zS65.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133023DXQSYFvTzh8OJuxy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133023x0paNty59IkOXUfM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330249ut6MFojNcGXJB0V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Percha by Rafael Fernández</h2>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这个名为 Percha 的口袋式支架很好地诠释了“有限的资源是如何通过优秀的创意得以解决生活上的问题”。支架的设计非常简单，可以很轻松地挂在挂钩或者门把上，无论是居家还是办公的场合都具有很高的实用性。每一个支架都由手工制作，售价为 57.77 美元，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/287837351/wall-hung-portable-magazine-rack-modern\">链接</a>进行购买，如果需要个性化上色等服务需要额外收取费用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330247RSTgpGieqCyc2lV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133024Pqr10eSs4bVT9Zx2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133025H7luYSJya6Od8s5r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330263MrOEhPli4UHxy5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330265gNK2m8SRkJh7Z6z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}